| Backend    | Baza        | Supabase, SQL, Edge Functions, RLS, auth       |
| Frontend   | Ekran       | React Native, Expo, UI, navigation, maps       |
| Scraper    | Skrejper    | Web scraping, Apify, data pipelines, AI parse  |
| Portal     | Portal      | Admin panel (Next.js), public website (Astro)  |
| Chronicle  | Hroni\u010dar    | Progress tracking, session logs, napkin         |

Each agent has rules in `.cursor/rules/[name].mdc`.
Chronicle maintains PROGRESS.md and .claude/napkin.md.

