## Reference Priority

When in doubt, consult in this order:
1. docs/hype-architecture-v5.md \u2014 All design decisions
2. docs/hype-supabase-schema.sql \u2014 DB schema (source of truth for data model)
3. docs/hype-scraping-architecture.md \u2014 Scraper pipeline code
4. docs/hype-scraper-validation.md \u2014 What works, what's broken
5. .claude/napkin.md \u2014 Learned mistakes and patterns
6. PROGRESS.md \u2014 Current status of all work
